  "faqQ1": "How do I create an account?",
  "faqA1": "Download the mySupplyCO app and tap \"Sign Up\". Enter your name, email, and mobile number. You'll receive a verification code. Enter it to complete registration.",
  "faqQ2": "How do I check stock availability?",
  "faqA2": "Once logged in, tap the \"Stock\" tab. You can view real-time inventory from your assigned supply center. Use the search bar to find specific items quickly.",
  "faqQ3": "Who can place orders?",
  "faqA3": "Government authorized officials registered with mySupplyCO can place orders. Your access level depends on your government organization and role.",
  "faqQ4": "How do I receive notifications?",
  "faqA4": "Go to Settings → Manage Alerts to enable/disable notifications for stock updates, order status, and system announcements. Push notifications require app permission.",
  "faqQ5": "Is there an offline mode?",
  "faqA5": "Yes! The app automatically caches recent stock data. You can view previously loaded stock information even without an internet connection.",
  "faqQ6": "How do I reset my password?",
  "faqA6": "On the login page, tap \"Forgot Password?\" and enter your registered email. You'll receive a reset link via email. Follow the instructions to create a new password.",
